*dracut-034-r1 (16 Oct 2013)

  16 Oct 2013; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@gentoo.org> +dracut-034-r1.ebuild,
  +files/034-0006-resume-fix-swap-detection-in-hostonly.patch:
